    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.4.25" />
     
                                                                                                                        <fw type="curatorial">25</fw>

                                            <fw type="letterhead">
                                                <hi rend="caps">
                                                       UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA
                                                            <lb/>
                                                        OFFICE OF THE PRESIDENT
                                                </hi>
                                            </fw>
            
                <opener>
                                                                                                    <dateline>Berkeley, October 8, 1917.</dateline>

                    <salute>My dear Mr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>It gives me pleasure to invite you to lecture at the University of California and give readings from your works on a date to be determined by your convenience. I should suggest an evening lecture. When you have sent to my office a statement of the date that will be acceptable to you, an auditorium will be reserved for you on that date.</p>
    
                <p>Professor John Galen Howard, of our Department of Architecture, has generously signified the intention of a group of your admirers in California to provide the honorarium for your lecture. I have told Professor Howard that this letter has been written to you.</p>
    
                <p>Looking forward to the pleasure of hearing you at this University, I am</p>
                <closer>
                                                    <salute>Faithfully yours,</salute>

                                                    <signed>Benj. <unclear>I.</unclear> Wheeler.</signed>

                    <address>
                        <addrLine>John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt, <hi rend="caps">LL.D.</hi>,</addrLine>
                            <addrLine>Bancroft, Nebraska.</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
